@baseGateway = http://localhost:4000


### Auth Register
POST {{baseGateway}}/auth/register
content-type: application/json

{
    "email": "anna.doe@example.com",
    "displayName": "anna Doe",
    "password": "Password123!"
}


### Auth Login
POST {{baseGateway}}/auth/login
content-type: application/json

{
    "email": "william.doe@example.com",
    "password": "Password123!"
}


### Media upload (multipart field name: file). Set @accessToken from login response.
@accessToken = REPLACE_ME
POST {{baseGateway}}/media
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="hello.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello from chat media
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--


### Media metadata
GET {{baseGateway}}/media/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001/info
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}